\b\fs28 Important Notice
\b0 : 
\b \cf4 Allocating and Filling Memory by elements of a structure is based on the sequence of each element. 
\b0 \cf0 For Example:\
\

\b First
\b0 : 
\f2 \cf2 member_name1
